PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of NEWFOUNDLAND of the administration and control over three parcels of land and land covered by water situate in the Town of BURGEO that contain a total area of some 5,430 square metres, which are to be used for marine and related purposes and to accommodate existing facilities.
